      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "EXCITING ZOEY (5) turned spotting a big start finishing sixth (18.36) last time in a Grade 5 at Richmond Straight. Has a good record here at this journey. Has ability and looks hard to stop. SANCTIMONIOUS (7) turned in a better effort at Richmond Straight last start, finishing third behind Twisted Toe (18.18) in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Expected to feature again. BERNARDO'S BELLE (2) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fifth (23.32) in a Grade 5 at this track. Yet to score from this box but has never missed the frame in two starts. Likely to play a prominent role. STAR ELISE (1) is right in the mix.",
